snippet.title: Little Elf Tanks - Stop Motion Trailer
snippet.description:
A bombastic bug busting adventure! Play as one of four playable characters in their quest to to free their fellow elves from the clutches of an evil army of spiders. If they crawl, blast em all! Let nothing stand in your way. 

Little Elf Tanks drives into Steam on January 17th 2024

Wishlist the game here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2330780/Little_Elf_Tanks/
